CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg 14 reads: "Auditing Department - Left to right: Joan Kranick, assistant bookkeeper; Edward Porter, lien search clerk; Mary Scatteregia, payroll clerk, and Janet Aiello, typist"
TitMainTitle: Joan Kranick, wearing hair in bun, Edward Porter, Mary Scatteregia, and Janet Aiello, gathered in Auditing Department of Allegheny County Prothonotary office with two desks and three lockers
